BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:6DABC051-D0C8-40E8-AA5A-F9A0EB1956E8:BAD69819-CC8E-44DA-8C32-3DE096CFC4B3@andy-combined
DTSTAMP:20260523T230431Z
DTSTART:20260519T233000Z
DTEND:20260520T003000Z
SUMMARY:SG Performance 
LOCATION:Strokes Gained Studio
DESCRIPTION:Our golf-specific classes allow you to choose a level of progra
 mming that suites your needs! Our expert coaches will assist you with choo
 sing the appropriate class based on your movement\, training history and e
 xperience. We have three golf-specific classes that run multiple times a d
 ay:- MOVE is designed to be all inclusive. If you are playing in pain or w
 e have identified you have a number of physical limitations in your physic
 al assessment then this program is for you! Lots of flexibility\, core and
  base level strength training forms the base of our Move program.- TRAIN i
 s designed for those who are looking to get stronger! If we have only iden
 tified a couple of limitations through our assessment and you have a base 
 level of strength and stability then this program is for you! You will see
  lots of base level strength and stability work with emphasis on being str
 ong through your body’s full range of movement!- PERFORM is designed for
  those who are looking to increase their club head speed and gain serious 
 metres off the tee! If you are moving well and we have identified a good b
 ase level of strength\, stability and movement then this program is for yo
 u! In this program you will see the introduction of more advanced strength
  based movements and some advanced power based movements to have you feeli
 ng stronger and more powerful than ever!
END:VEVENT
